The '''''Happy Hutt''''' was one of the 600 refugee ships the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] used as [[Human/Legends|Human]] shields in the [[Battle of Coruscant (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Coruscant]]. It was carrying 5,000 refugees from [[Ralltiir/Legends|Ralltiir]].

